      <title>A message from @eobofficial: I have a new solo album coming out on 22nd May. It ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DV_IY5zjAf7/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DV_IY5zjAf7/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652765451_886044817770760_5171870049393475269_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDgzNjcwMTc2MDA2MzQ4Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=PUTwYjecXlsQ7kNvwHjo4r-&amp;_nc_oc=AdovIpyhXZUYQAqnE82JqZ-y7gN_qhGBh-t0WFDCiGiof1M1nPdE7ciPKCsiBkMigmE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9cV9h4Ba1xNA_Aq96yVuAA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afzg2_xceRrfBdCKpw0eFx57NrL61iJnQmA21edqKTf2yA&amp;oe=69CA31C8" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @radiohead" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@radiohead</strong></p><p>A message from @eobofficial:<br/>
<br/>
I have a new solo album coming out on 22nd May. It is called Blue Morpho - pre-order at the link in profile.<br/>
<br/>
It was co-written and produced with @paulepworth and @riley_mac, and mixed by @benbaptie. Artwork by @brojazz. I’m so grateful for the extraordinary players who helped make it come alive - @philipselway, @dave_okumu_, @eskaonline, @shabakahutchings, @nrammmusic, @dansee28, Crispin Spry Robinson, @yvesfernandez, Luke Mullen, and others. Musicians whose presence changes everything.<br/>
<br/>
A single - also called Blue Morpho - is out today, with a video.<br/>
<br/>
There’s a short film too, shot in Wales, where much of the album was written, recorded and dreamt up. These songs came out of a dark place, but as Wendell Berry writes, ‘the dark, too, blooms and sings, and is traveled by dark feet and dark wings.’ There was deep beauty and a profound sense of grace in that place.<br/>
<br/>
I’m pleased to announce that there will be screening events for the film held in London - 24th March, Paris - 25th March and Oxford - 26th March. Sign up to my mailing list - link in profile - for a chance to attend London or Paris. Tickets for Oxford on sale soon.<br/>
<br/>
Later in the year, we will be playing these songs live. We would love to share them with you in a room somewhere out there.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you.<br/>
<br/>
With love and gratitude,<br/>
<br/>
🙏 Ed</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQM1sxgcWd0PdY3LDY12N1TiHQ_nA9WJa35DIfqVeR1p4TRL1c448Ohw5Gx5icQKZBd0LnTDtiHkXVoOXTsJ7OlI.mp4?strext=1&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=EmbofXDbE4oQ7kNvwHj9Exf&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTc5NTAzMTg4OTkxMTY2NjIsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjo4LCJ2aV91c2VjYXNlX2lkIjoxMDA5OSwiZHVyYXRpb25fcyI6MjgsInVybGdlbl9zb3VyY2UiOiJ3d3cifQ%3D%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=b6cc54979f9195c4&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=9cV9h4Ba1xNA_Aq96yVuAA&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Afy2OuPrDTie8KeqXjB_I34EyPMXtgodgpeRT-oYVipQ4g&amp;oe=69CA44EF">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DV_IY5zjAf7/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
