      <title>Jonny is back with @shyebentzur and the Rajasthan Express for their new album, R...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVq27WhDO9W/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVq27WhDO9W/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649228792_18446840053110762_7397682964199296542_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0OTEzMDQwNDY3OTA1MzE0MjE4NDQ2ODQwMDUwMTEwNzYy.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwMTR4MTgwMi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=H_PDCeWVKM4Q7kNvwEtSmxc&amp;_nc_oc=Adq-XzrffpKfa-mReY8eSoFDbq2-r50jxYK3s92i-_RpXpxjlDt4N3jgnhPcOAND6WI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9cV9h4Ba1xNA_Aq96yVuAA&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfxZXbgbjwO4D7Q95ATRSDBP6ESW5i-G3Bgwb8qV12n7nQ&amp;oe=69CA17DF" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @radiohead" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@radiohead</strong></p><p>Jonny is back with @shyebentzur and the Rajasthan Express for their new album, Ranjha, to be released through @world_circuit_records on 8th May 2026, together with first single Ranjha. <br/>
<br/>
Produced by @sampettsdavies and recorded at Jonny’s Oxfordshire studio, Ranjha is the follow-up to the critically acclaimed Junun, which recently had its tenth anniversary. <br/>
<br/>
Ranjha is available to pre-order at the link in profile on CD, download and a special red and coral splatter gatefold vinyl with a limited edition signed print. In addition, Ranjha and Junun come together with a 32-page newspaper zine with imagery spanning the two records and an essay from Jonny about the project.<br/>
<br/>
The title track Ranjha is accompanied by a short film made by Ian Patrick and you can find it at the link in profile.</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQOR3N9TPZL2H7WwituekEuJ8wbjtPEcW2tDKW-O3vZ-UjJAWhZRrzIMW4dDnPyVt0ykpIzJr4W1ZMY8RPVftz_a.mp4?strext=1&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=lpGn8BZkyvAQ7kNvwHe0rgm&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTc5NDgzMDI1NzUxMTY2NjIsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjoxNiwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjE4LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=18e064f229e26e64&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=9cV9h4Ba1xNA_Aq96yVuAA&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwCkwHRXzzpz3ffCXA7KIgpFwl_a0Xmj_ZJaRlyGfmiYw&amp;oe=69CA231A">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVq27WhDO9W/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
